<tbody>
<tr style="height: 49px;">
<td style="width: 11.0709%; height: 49px;">V</td>
<td style="width: 88.9291%; height: 49px;">Volatile</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 49px;">
<td style="width: 11.0709%; height: 49px;">U</td>
<td style="width: 88.9291%; height: 49px;">Uncertainty</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 49px;">
<td style="width: 11.0709%; height: 49px;">C</td>
<td style="width: 88.9291%; height: 49px;">Complex</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 49px;">
<td style="width: 11.0709%; height: 49px;">A</td>
<td style="width: 88.9291%; height: 49px;">Ambiguous</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>What can we do to mitigate V.U.C.A?</p>
